node.text: What a day!! Thank you @tedx_glasgow so grateful for this opportunity to share my story further and wider. I was so nervous waiting to go on stage but once I stood on that red dot I knew it wasn’t about me talking but who was listening. Speaking out for all those who can’t find their voice yet ✊💛 #tedxgla2019 #ted #tedtalks #MADTalks #Unbroken #nomoreshame #metoo #speakingout #findyourvoice #endthesilence
You are a beautiful light if inspiration! 💜
You are such a beautiful and inspiring person . So lovely to meet you x x
You were inspirational... thank you for sharing your story.
love your feed! DM us, lets get you some gear!
